data.description: Welcome to your new home on a quaint street in central OKC with easy access to shopping and restaurants. The home has been respectfully updated keeping the historic charm intact while offering modern touches throughout. As you walk in you'll find a beautiful airy living space with vaulted ceilings perfect for entertaining leading into the dining area and breakfast nook. The fully renovated kitchen is absolutely stunning offering plenty of storage, beautiful countertops and includes all new appliances. The large hall offers access to three spacious bedrooms and fully updated bathrooms including new tile work, shower install, cabinetry, light fixtures and more. Downstairs you'll find your dream flex space that can double as a bonus room or bedroom along with ample amount of storage and laundry room. Beautiful outdoor space in the backyard with a large deck, outdoor kitchen bar and rock patio. Two car garage/storage in back.
